                p.large
                  | At Wild Willy's, we Guarantee THE BEST QUALITY possible in event coordination, equipment, professionalism and committment to ensuring your guests have a great time at your event
          .column.is-6
            .is-feature-right
              h2.mb-30(data-aos='fade-up', data-aos-delay='0') What Set's Us Apart
              .feature-content(data-aos='fade-left', data-aos-delay='200')
                p.large-bullet.mb-20
                  img.bullet(src='img/icon-bullet.png')
                  | Highest Quality Equipment
                p.large-bullet.mb-20
                  img.bullet(src='img/icon-bullet.png')
